law.history: Repealed 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 169, sec. 8, effective January 1, 2008. -- Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 310, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 149, sec. 4, effective June 17, 1954.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Nonresident owner or operator of watercraft to furnish description of property and of route or system traversed.
